title: The #1 Key to Break Your Scarcity Mindset

description:
Episode 666 - Your scarcity mindset is holding you back from all of the treasures you want in this world. In this podcast I am going to teach you a very simple strategy to break that scarcity mindset, so that you can see the world through a lens of abundance.
